=== 球赛组织者和球具生产商 ===
尼克劳斯还是PGA巡回赛重要赛事“纪念高球赛”的创始人，这项赛事在他的家乡俄亥俄州繆菲德村（{{lang|en|Muirfield Village}}）举办，并在他亲自设计的球场进行。这一赛事的前身是哥伦比亚职业业余混合赛（于1975年停办）。<ref>{{cite book |title=Jack Nicklaus: My Story |year=2007 |url=https://archive.org/details/jacknicklausmyst0000nick_h4i0 |publisher=Simon & Schuster Paperbacks |author=Nicklaus, Jack |coauthor=Bowden, Ken |page=[https://archive.org/details/jacknicklausmyst0000nick_h4i0/page/344 344]-345 |ISBN=1416542248|language=en}}</ref>。此外，尼克劳斯名下的“尼克劳斯高尔夫球装备”公司创立于1992年<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.manta.com/coms2/dnbcompany_649gsp |accessdate=2009-10-30 |title=Nicklaus Golf Equipment Company Profile |language=en |archive-date=2015-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017151145/http://www.manta.com/coms2/dnbcompany_649gsp |dead-url=no }}</ref>，主要以三个品牌生产销售高尔夫球装备用具:金熊版（{{lang|en|Golden Bear}}）、 傑克·尼克勞斯簽名版（{{lang|en|Jack Nicklaus Signature}}）和尼克勞斯超值版（{{lang|en|Nicklaus Premium}}）。这三个品牌分别面向不同层次的高尔夫球手<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nicklaus-golf.com/index.html |title=Nicklaus Golf Equipment |accessdate=2009-10-30 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080514192856/http://www.nicklaus-golf.com/index.html |archive-date=2008-05-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

== 竞技风格 ==
尼克劳斯是同时期球员中击球距离最长和线路最直的选手之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/8534978/ |title=Ball-striking |accessdate=2009-10-30 |publisher=NBC Sports |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081023120825/http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/8534978/ |archive-date=2008-10-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他通常喜欢打出右曲球，以使球可以在光滑的果岭上较快地减速。选择这一技术动作的另一个原因是他的击球水平能保证他击出足够远的距离<ref>{{cite book|last=Nicklaus |first=Jack |coauthors=Bowden, Ken |title=Golf My Way |url=https://archive.org/details/golfmyway0000jack |page=[https://archive.org/details/golfmyway0000jack/page/28 28] |publisher=William Heinemann Ltd |year=1974 |isbn=1850514755|language=en}}</ref>。尼克劳斯也以其对球场的利用技巧而著称。他往往能够合理利用地形，让自己的每一杆球都为下一杆做好成功的铺垫。[[加里·普莱尔|加里·普莱尔]]曾盛赞其击球理念是“有史以来最伟大的”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/8534977/ |title=Course Management |accessdate=2009-10-30 |publisher=NBC Sports |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081023120814/http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/8534977/ |archive-date=2008-10-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。尽管尼克劳斯的推杆技术并不是最出色的，但他往往能在关键时刻把握机会，推出漂亮的致胜一球<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/8534970/ |title=Putting |accessdate=2009-10-30 |publisher=NBC Sports |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081025094005/http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/8534970/ |archive-date=2008-10-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他的稳健风格也是球手中较为出名的，在不必要的时候很少愿意打冒险球。尤其是在果岭上，他往往选择稳健保守，用两杆推杆来确保成绩。对此，尼克劳斯在自传中写道：“我是一名优秀的两杆推球手，但有时会显得过于保守。”<ref>{{cite book |title=Jack Nicklaus: My Story |year=2007 |url=https://archive.org/details/jacknicklausmyst0000nick_h4i0 |publisher=Simon & Schuster Paperbacks |author=Nicklaus, Jack |coauthor=Bowden, Ken |page=[https://archive.org/details/jacknicklausmyst0000nick_h4i0/page/268 268] |ISBN=1416542248|language=en}}</ref>。

== 荣誉 ==
1962年PGA巡回赛季结束后，首次参赛的尼克劳斯就获得了组织方颁发的[[PGA巡回赛最佳新人|PGA巡回赛最佳新人]]荣誉。在获得五次PGA巡回赛年度最佳球手和八次PGA巡回赛奖金榜冠军之余，他还获得了[[鲍勃·琼斯奖|鲍勃·琼斯奖]]和[[佩恩·斯图尔特奖|佩恩·斯图尔特奖]]等荣誉。他还被列入[[世界高尔夫球名人堂|世界高尔夫球名人堂]]和[[加拿大高尔夫球名人堂|加拿大高尔夫球名人堂]]。他的肖像还被印刷于[[苏格兰皇家银行|苏格兰皇家银行]]的五镑纸币上，从而成为首位在世期间被印在[[英镑|英国纸币]]上的皇室人物以外的名人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rbs.com/about03.asp?id=ABOUT_US/OUR_HERITAGE/OUR_HISTORY/OUR_BANKNOTES/COMMEMORATIVE_BANKNOTES|title=Commemorative Banknotes|publisher=The Royal Bank of Scotland|accessdate=2009-10-30|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081125022143/https://www.rbs.com/about03.asp?id=ABOUT_US%2FOUR_HERITAGE%2FOUR_HISTORY%2FOUR_BANKNOTES%2FCOMMEMORATIVE_BANKNOTES|archivedate=2008-11-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rampantscotland.com/letter2005b.htm|title=High Fives for Golden Bear|date=2005-12-24|publisher=Rampant Scotland|accessdate=2009-10-30|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815170208/http://www.rampantscotland.com/letter2005b.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在他的家乡俄亥俄州哥伦布市的[[俄亥俄州立大学|俄亥俄州立大学]]校园内，建有杰克·尼克劳斯纪念馆<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nicklausmuseum.org/ |title=Nicklaus Museum |publisher=NicklausMuseum.com |accessdate=2009-10-30 |language=en |archive-date=2016-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160220052459/http://www.nicklausmuseum.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他还获邀参加该校著名的行进乐团表演，当成员们排列成标志性的Ohio字样时，构成i上一点的人就是尼克劳斯，这是对于乐团外成员的最高荣誉<ref>{{cite news | url=http://sports.espn.go.com/ncf/news/story?id=2641971 | title=Strike up the band: Nicklaus dots 'i' at Ohio State | date=2006-10-28 | publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]], via [[ESPN|ESPN.com]] | language=en | accessdate=2009-10-15 | archive-date=2015-10-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017151145/http://sports.espn.go.com/ncf/news/story?id=2641971 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

